structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
GENERAL PROVISIONS APPLICABLE TO COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.catch_line: Authority of KRS 65.680 to 65.699 supplemental to other legal authority.
law.text: The authority granted by KRS 65.680 to 65.699 is in addition to and not a limitation on any other authorizations granted by or pursuant to law for the same or similar purposes.
law.history: Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 358, sec. 10, effective July 14, 2000.
